    question: 'Sequenzy or Drip for cart recovery?',
    answer: 'Choose Sequenzy when Shopify teams wanting agent-first lifecycle strategy without enterprise bloat. Choose Drip when Teams wanting visual workflows and behavior-based segmentation. Sequenzy still leads as lifecycle layer if neither owns strategy.',
